{"tid":2129540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警是日金句：「止暴制亂係需要勇氣」","createTime":"2020-07-28T16:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T18:25:12.000Z","uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d4757e2f67fba9f19a47ca99e5909a07bf8270","tid":2129540,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"去年8月3日的「旺角再遊行」，入夜後有大批示威者於旺角區設置路障，9人被控非法集結罪，今日（28日）在九龍城裁判法院續審。負責制服第八被告的「速龍」成員今日作供語出驚人，多番引起大狀和被告竊笑、嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n隸屬於機動部隊總部的警長430方樂文，當晚以特別戰術小隊成員（俗稱「速龍」）的身份執勤。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n方作供時強調有人向警方投擲水樽，辯方質疑水樽會令方分心，而不能如方自稱的視線沒有離開過被告。方稱自己並未有理會水樽，因「我哋（警察）成日都俾人掉水樽、掉磚。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方追問，會否擔心水樽內的不明液體會濺到警員。方表示，僅看到水樽落在他的前方。辯方遂質疑，方的自然反應會閃躲迎面而來的水樽<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">，方回應：「止暴制亂係需要勇氣」、「如果因為危險我就唔執法，我就唔係警察啦。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075925&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=31ab9ed8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075925&h=d63af41a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075925</a>"},{"pid":"c8a02feb63b70549a88b7a75ebed30adac741321","tid":2129540,"uid":321059,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"「止暴制亂係需要勇氣」<br />\n「如果因為危險我就唔執法，我就唔係警察啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qvrZDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qvrZDo.jpg&h=e3e972e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad0e8db5e99d8bba9ba8249858e714c74f0393f3","tid":2129540,"uid":3241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"721果兩條軍裝拖左去打杷未"},{"pid":"18cf7d81f0331f4964a6d21c9db6d7ca44332ebf","tid":2129540,"uid":134438,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">「如果因為危險我就唔屠殺猶太人，我就唔係納粹黨衛軍啦。」</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cd8f433d503351f348dfab1ca2b926fd6e54efb4","tid":2129540,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8a02feb63b70549a88b7a75ebed30adac741321","tid":2129540,"uid":321059,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"「止暴制亂係需要勇氣」<br />\n「如果因為危險我就唔執法，我就唔係警察啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qvrZDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qvrZDo.jpg&h=e3e972e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"林卓廷早幾日都發現左幾件無勇氣逃兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25f729110b22e502db9c65c0b2e908ba27f6750","tid":2129540,"uid":14422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"但連露樣嘅勇氣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bF3ttxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbF3ttxj.jpg&h=fddb8cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fcd2d9787b9777c7d54c2cc6ced54cf140c132d","tid":2129540,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"諗諗吓個標題應該改做<br />\n<br />\n黑警是日笑話"},{"pid":"7e767452e00ac51cc991b185ea91badead0ed6ff","tid":2129540,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e25f729110b22e502db9c65c0b2e908ba27f6750","tid":2129540,"uid":14422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"但連露樣嘅勇氣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bF3ttxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbF3ttxj.jpg&h=fddb8cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim